WEBVTT

01:37.850 --> 01:41.000
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.090 --> 01:44.000
[Episode 38]

01:55.229 --> 01:58.979
[Ruang Rapat]

02:01.290 --> 02:02.830
[Direktur Wei]

03:01.750 --> 03:02.630
